# Development containers (don't include in standalone builds)
# In Codespaces/devcontainer builds we need a few files from `.devcontainer/` (entrypoint, setup, requirements).
# Keep the folder excluded by default, but re-include only the files needed when building the dev image.
.devcontainer/
.devcontainer_orig/

# Re-include devcontainer build assets required by Docker build
!.devcontainer/
!.devcontainer/entrypoint.sh
!.devcontainer/setup-db.sh
!.devcontainer/requirements.in
!.devcontainer/requirements-dev.in
!.devcontainer/devcontainer.json
!.devcontainer/Dockerfile

